#: ../../../source/docs/api_reference/bind.h.rst:538
msgid ""
"Class constructor for objects that use a factory function to create the "
"object.  This method will accept either a function pointer, ``std::"
"function`` object or function object which will return a newly constructed "
"object.  When the ``Callable`` is a function object the function signature "
"must be explicitly specified in the ``Signature`` template parameter in the "
"format ``ReturnType (Args...)``.  For ``Callable`` types other than function "
"objects the method signature will be deduced."
msgstr ""

